{"tid":790372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果填海地全部用嚟起公屋，請馬上填!  如果唔係，就咪撚填!","createTime":"2018-08-23T03:12:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T05:29:18.000Z","uid":83913,"like":13,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f315358a0b7d791531d60ef2a93623ad9fda6ad9","tid":790372,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T03:12:17.000Z","msg":"成日話無地無地，要填海<br />\n<br />\n但開發完啲新市鎮公屋比例又咁低<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔係環保撚，但你填撚完海，移撚完山，<br />\n<br />\n原來又唔係真心造屋俾窮撚香港人<br />\n<br />\n咁你就咪撚用房屋需求嚟做藉口啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n直接話想填多啲地俾地產商發展好過啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好撚多人又真係信撚晒架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講真，發展啲新市鎮公屋比例咪又奇低，係蠢人至信<br />\n<br />\n如果移撚完山,填撚完海都根本唔會有屋俾我住，<br />\n<br />\n咁不如留返個海景俾我睇下<br />\n<br />\n留返個乾淨既海俾啲魚遊下算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fdc9aacdf2979d7d4684b282f7e1e302c131c6f","tid":790372,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T03:20:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d149fa4f8dded2245324f8d74aab153503d9c5f","tid":790372,"uid":18702,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T03:20:38.000Z","msg":"其實起撚完啲公屋都唔會俾香港人住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af845979dc30c856f0408487670a1c6950faf55b","tid":790372,"uid":107927,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T03:21:08.000Z","msg":"填海起公屋俾中國新移民住?<br />\n取消每日150中國新移民來香港先"},{"pid":"0551cdfe7afd571c66fc4202de383658ccc4b238","tid":790372,"uid":58307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T03:39:52.000Z","msg":"公屋依個年代申請到係得果150件，正常人撚申請到咩屌。填完咪撚起公屋！益左班大陸西"},{"pid":"e08a1439ecbe5d1332f9492d91d3203b6b43f5cd","tid":790372,"uid":150466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"r